ers will assess your communication skills, personality traits, job fitment, and overall suitability for face-to-face interaction.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>However, performing well in the online test to get interviewed. Then, you must clear the interview successfully to get the final job offer from TCS BPS. Stay prepared for this two-stage process.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"important-links-tcs-bps-exam\">Important Links- TCS BPS Exam <\/h2>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/tcs-bps-hiring-process\/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"9742\">TCS BPS Hiring Process 2024 For Freshers<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/tcs-bps-eligibility-criteria\/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"9476\">TCS BPS Eligibility Criteria 2024, Qualification, Percentage, Backlog<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/tcs-bps-apply-online\/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"9325\">TCS BPS Apply Online 2024,  Application Link<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/tcs-bps-syllabus\/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"9620\">TCS BPS Syllabus 2024 and Exam Pattern, Download PDF<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/tcs-bps-interview-questions\/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"9762\">Top 10 TCS BPS Interview Questions and Answers 2024<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>In conclusion, this is an excellent opportunity for fresh graduates from the Arts, Commerce, and Science streams to kickstart their careers with a leading IT company like TCS. The TCS BPS division is rapidly expanding and hiring for various roles that can accelerate your professional growth right after college. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, you must ensure you meet all the eligibility criteria and register properly before the 26th April 2024 deadline. Stay prepared for the two-stage selection process involving an online written test and interviews. Clear both rounds successfully to get hired into exciting job roles at TCS BPS. Don&#8217;t miss this golden chance to be part of TCS&#8217; remarkable success story. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"tcs-bps-hiring-2024-fa-qs\">TCS BPS Hiring 2024 -FAQs<\/h2>\n\n\n<div id=\"rank-math-faq\" class=\"rank-math-block\">\n<div class=\"rank-math-list \">\n<div id=\"faq-question-1713423102199\" class=\"rank-math-list-item\">\n<h4 class=\"rank-math-question \">Q1. What is BPS&#8217;s role in TCS?<\/h4>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p>Ans. At TCS, Business Process Services (BPS) involve handling, various business operations. We use our expertise to manage tasks, accounts, HR, and supply- chain management across different industries, ensuring smooth operations and providing valuable insights.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"faq-question-1713423111921\" class=\"rank-math-list-item\">\n<h4 class=\"rank-math-question \">Q2.What is the salary of BPS jobs in TCS?<\/h4>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p>Ans. The typical salary for Business Process Services (BPS) employees at TCS in Bangalore ranges from \u20b91.8 Lakhs to \u20b94.5 Lakhs per year. On average, employees with 1 to 4 years of experience earn around \u20b92.7 Lakhs annually, based on data from 12 recent salaries.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"faq-question-1713423120506\" class=\"rank-math-list-item\">\n<h4 class=\"rank-math-question \">Q3.What is TCS BPS eligibility?<\/h4>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p>Ans. Graduates with degrees in B. Com, BA, BAF, BBI, BBA, BBM, BMS, and BSc (in various disciplines) who will pass out in 2024, to apply for full-time positions at TCS. Candidates must not have any pending backlogs when participating in the TCS selection process.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"faq-question-1713423133153\" class=\"rank-math-list-item\">\n<h4 class=\"rank-math-question \">Q4.What is the dress code in TCS BPS?<\/h4>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p>Ans. Wear long-sleeved shirts with formal pants or skirts in solid colors, or opt for knee-length kurtas or sarees. Complete the look with formal shoes like flats, heels, or dress sandals.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"faq-question-1713423146757\" class=\"rank-math-list-item\">\n<h4 class=\"rank-math-question \">Q5.Is the TCS BPS exam easy?<\/h4>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p>Ans. Candidates have less than 2 minutes for each   TCS BPS Quantitative Aptitude Section, and it&#8217;s known to be moderate to highly challenging. The topics covered include HCF &amp; LCM, Number Systems, and Geometry.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"faq-question-1713423157109\" class=\"rank-math-list-item\">\n<h4 class=\"rank-math-question \">Q6.What is TCS BPS&#8217;s full form?<\/h4>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p>Ans. TCS BPS offers non-IT and business process services, covering various industry-specific tasks like finance and accounting. Their services include combining core processes with analytics and insights to enhance enterprise operations.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"faq-question-1713423172655\" class=\"rank-math-list-item\">\n<h4 class=\"rank-math-question \">Q7.Does TCS BPS provide work from home?<\/h4>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p>Ans. Tata Consultancy Services (TCS) will no longer allow employees to work from home and,  must come to the office for all five working days. This means everyone has to be in the office from Monday to Friday.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"faq-question-1713423180315\" class=\"rank-math-list-item\">\n<h4 class=\"rank-math-question \">Q8.Which is better BPO or BPS?<\/h4>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p>Ans. While BPO service delivery typically handled simpler tasks, BPS now covers nearly all aspects of your business when necessary. It can extend to various areas to meet the diverse needs of your business operations.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"faq-question-1713779298245\" class=\"rank-m